nnoremap <silent><leader>xtl :call <SID>TestRun("Last", 0)<CR>
nnoremap <silent><leader>xtd :call <SID>TestDebugNearest()<CR>
nnoremap <silent><leader>xts :call <SID>TestSnapshot()<CR>
